title: Create an Aws S3 Bucket Using Terraform
tags: @zettel terraform aws _method
roam-id: feb1a6ce-6e90-4da4-8bad-a2c035abd1f9
type: text/markdown

``` hcl
provider "aws" {
  region = "us-east-1"
}

resource "aws_s3_bucket" "my_bucket" {
  bucket = "some-unique-name-980480"
  acl = "private"

  tags = {
    Environment = "dev"
    Owner = "you"
  }
}
```
